00:52:32.950 --> 00:52:38.240
this is that very important that people understand
your business model, up front. Because if

00:52:38.240 --> 00:52:42.000
it's like free and there is no apparent business
model, they're rightly suspicious that you

00:52:42.000 --> 00:52:45.089
